Technical Stack Details

Backend Stack:

Framework: ASP.NET Core 6.0+ (LTS)
Database: SQL Server 2019+ / Azure SQL
ORM: Entity Framework Core 6.0+
Caching: Redis / MemoryCache
Queue: Azure Service Bus / RabbitMQ
Search: Elasticsearch / Azure Search
File Storage: Azure Blob Storage / AWS S3
Email: SendGrid / Amazon SES
SMS: Twilio / Amazon SNS
Payment: Stripe / PayPal API
Authentication: ASP.NET Identity + JWT
API Documentation: Swagger/OpenAPI
Logging: Serilog + Application Insights
Testing: xUnit, Moq, FluentAssertions

Frontend Stack:

Framework: ASP.NET Core MVC with Razor Pages
UI Framework: Bootstrap 5 + custom CSS
JavaScript: ES6+ with module bundling
Charts: Chart.js / D3.js
Rich Text Editor: Quill.js / TinyMCE
File Upload: Dropzone.js / Uppy
Date Picker: Flatpickr
Validation: jQuery Validation + custom
Real-time: SignalR client
PWA: Service Workers + Manifest
Build Tool: Webpack / Vite
Testing: Jest / Playwright

DevOps Stack:

Version Control: Git (GitHub/GitLab/Azure DevOps)
CI/CD: GitHub Actions / Azure DevOps Pipelines
Containerization: Docker + Docker Compose
Orchestration: Kubernetes (optional)
Infrastructure: Azure / AWS (Infrastructure as Code)
Monitoring: Application Insights / New Relic
Error Tracking: Sentry / Raygun
Performance: Lighthouse / WebPageTest
Security: Snyk / SonarQube
